Package: r.bioc.singlecell.manifest
Type: Package
Title: Dependency manifest for the midas r-bioc-singlecell base image
Version: 0.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("DoM-MIDAS", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "noreply@midas.local")
Description: Declares the R and
    Bioconductor stack baked into the ghcr.io/dom-midas/r-bioc-singlecell
    image; The Dockerfile installs
    these with pak against the PPM snapshot and Bioconductor release
    pinned in the Dockerfile, producing the image.  
    packages.txt at $R_LIBS_SITE captures the exact versions.
